profile:
C-Star Roofing is a specialty roofing and siding contractor serving the commercial and residential markets since 1993. We are family owned roofing company licensed and insured in the Province of Ontario.

Our experienced personnel provides free estimate, roof inspections and detailed proposals. We provide high quality materials and 10 years labor warranty to ensure that you are 100% satisfied with our services. Our crews are experienced and professionally trained in the installation and repair and jobsite safety.

C-Star Roofing Inc will always provide top quality roofing job in the lowest cost. Our commitment and experience is our promise!

profile:
Full service general contractor with specialized crews offering the following services: Wheelchair accessibility conversion and designs for homes and businesses, GAF Master Elite Roofing, Certified VELUX Skylight and Sun Tunnel installation specialist, windows, doors, siding, environmentally friendly attic insulation, soffit/fascia/trough, custom bathroom renovations, commercial drywall and project management. Voted #1 contracting company in Durham Region 2009, 2010 and 2011 by Durham Business Times. Received the 2010 & 2013 Business Excellence Award of the year from the Ajax-Pickering Board of Trade. Received the City of Pickering Access Award for Disability Issues 2014. Habitat for Humanity.
For all your home repair/ renovation needs, please book an appointment with one of our qualified customer representatives.

profile: Longley Roofing is a family owned and operated business dedicated to providing you with an honest, transparent  and educational experience. We take a personalized service approach with all our clients. We love to talk shop, show pictures and get our drones in the air. We take a consultative approach to serving  our clients, offering ideas on process and materials. Before, During and After Photos/ Videos are taken for all our jobs and will be  provided at the end of each project. Longley Roofing strives to not just meet but exceed the expectations of our clients.
